OL,3,CTeenager buried without his heart
OL,4,Cafter an alleged hit-and-run in
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,FHis mum, Nicola Gardner, said her son
OL,8,Fwas "left like a dog to die in the
OL,9,Froad".
OL,11,FJust hours before Harry's funeral on 6
OL,12,FJanuary, Nicola discovered that
OL,13,FSpanish authorities had retained his
OL,14,Fheart for further testing. He was
OL,15,Fburied in Anfield without the organ.
