OL,4,Cafter an alleged hit-and-run in
OL,5,CTenerife
OL,7,FInvestigators informed the family the
OL,8,Fheart was being preserved as part of a
OL,9,F"criminal death" inquiry, though
OL,10,FNicola believes further tests are
OL,11,Funnecessary given the confirmed cause
OL,12,Fof death.
OL,14,FThe family have criticised the
OL,15,Fhandling of the investigation,
OL,16,Faccusing Spanish officials of poor
OL,17,Fcommunication and slow progress.
