OL,7,FThey also faced significant delays
OL,8,Fwith paperwork ` with the Coroner's
OL,9,FOffice for Liverpool and Wirral not
OL,10,Fnotified of Harry's death until New
OL,11,FYear's Eve, nearly a month after the
OL,12,Ftragedy.
OL,14,FHarry, the youngest of four brothers,
OL,15,Fhad lived in Tenerife for 18 months
OL,16,Fbefore his death. Nicola described him
OL,17,Fas "caring, lovely and funny".
